UserHookEvent

UserJoinEvent

UserQuitEvent
This event is fired when a user quits the server at the eyes of the plugin.
UserUnHookEvent
This event is fired when the plugin unhooks a player, this event can happen when the server is stopped, or when the plugin is about to be updated.
